org.apache.flink.api.java.operators.join

类 JoinOperatorSetsBase<I1,I2>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.java.operators.join.JoinOperatorSetsBase<I1,I2>
  • 类型参数:
    I1 - The type of the first input DataSet of the Join transformation.
    I2 - The type of the second input DataSet of the Join transformation.
    直接已知子类:
    JoinOperator.JoinOperatorSets

    @Public
public class JoinOperatorSetsBase<I1,I2>
extends Object
    Intermediate step of an Outer Join transformation.
    To continue the Join transformation, select the join key of the first input DataSet by calling where(int...) or where(KeySelector).

    • 方法详细资料

      • where

        public JoinOperatorSetsBase.JoinOperatorSetsPredicateBase where(int... fields)
        Continues a Join transformation.
        Defines the Tuple fields of the first join DataSet that should be used as join keys.
        Note: Fields can only be selected as join keys on Tuple DataSets.
        参数:
        fields - The indexes of the other Tuple fields of the first join DataSets that should be used as keys.
        返回:
        An incomplete Join transformation. Call JoinOperatorSetsBase.JoinOperatorSetsPredicateBase.equalTo(int...) or JoinOperatorSetsBase.JoinOperatorSetsPredicateBase.equalTo(KeySelector) to continue the Join.
        另请参阅:
        Tuple, DataSet

      • where

        public JoinOperatorSetsBase.JoinOperatorSetsPredicateBase where(String... fields)
        Continues a Join transformation.
        Defines the fields of the first join DataSet that should be used as grouping keys. Fields are the names of member fields of the underlying type of the data set.
        参数:
        fields - The fields of the first join DataSets that should be used as keys.
        返回:
        An incomplete Join transformation. Call JoinOperatorSetsBase.JoinOperatorSetsPredicateBase.equalTo(int...) or JoinOperatorSetsBase.JoinOperatorSetsPredicateBase.equalTo(KeySelector) to continue the Join.
        另请参阅:
        Tuple, DataSet

      • where

        public <K> JoinOperatorSetsBase.JoinOperatorSetsPredicateBase where(org.apache.flink.api.java.functions.KeySelector<I1,K> keySelector)
        Continues a Join transformation and defines a KeySelector function for the first join DataSet.
        The KeySelector function is called for each element of the first DataSet and extracts a single key value on which the DataSet is joined.
        参数:
        keySelector - The KeySelector function which extracts the key values from the DataSet on which it is joined.
        返回:
        An incomplete Join transformation. Call JoinOperatorSetsBase.JoinOperatorSetsPredicateBase.equalTo(int...) or JoinOperatorSetsBase.JoinOperatorSetsPredicateBase.equalTo(KeySelector) to continue the Join.
        另请参阅:
        KeySelector, DataSet
